                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-28-off119 t17890422-28-cd120"></join>, 32 lb. weight of lead, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890422-28-victim280" type="victimName">
